---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="象棋规则 - 相弈象棋" description="中国象棋规则和残局练习说明。" canonicalPath="/rules/">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Rules</p>
      <h1>象棋规则</h1>
      <div class="info-grid">
        <article class="content-panel"><h3>棋盘与九宫</h3><p>双方在九宫内保护将帅，并通过车马炮兵等子力争夺局面。</p></article>
        <article class="content-panel"><h3>常见胜负</h3><p>将死、困毙、认输或超时都会影响棋局结果。</p></article>
        <article class="content-panel"><h3>残局练习</h3><p>残局适合训练计算力和基本杀法，是提升棋力的重要入口。</p></article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
